{"tid":1626243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[全民休息日?] 一句講晒，今晚休唔休？","createTime":"2019-10-05T10:19:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T11:28:08.000Z","uid":255092,"like":21,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"11514963febd91f224ba2cd16df522151e9bfe6a","tid":1626243,"uid":255092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:19:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">蒙面法第一個夜晚，你休唔休？<br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽話，休！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 片地開花，唔休！</span>"},{"pid":"0ef01d33a660a1fd8c37e8e13441e46152b7cb38","tid":1626243,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:19:55.000Z","msg":"【行動】商戶蝕大本對政府怨氣重！大家係時候出手connect沉默的中小企！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1625700\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1625700</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n隨著政府不斷挑釁香港人，火上加油，導致抗爭越演越烈。<span style=\"color: red;\"> 反送中持續了一百多日，警察胡亂鎮壓，亂放催淚彈，對地區造成嘅滋擾，無人幫襯對佢地來講造成極大損失。<br />\n<strong>依家開始有唔少藍絲或扮中立嘅商人對政府及警察產生怨言。</strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請大家利用呢個機會，廣泛向商戶宣傳，爭取商戶棄暗投明，企起香港人一方，或至少唔再支持政府、警察，以及港共保皇黨。</span></strong><br />\n請推我個post以了解當中嘅行動策略。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1625700\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1625700</a>"},{"pid":"012bef687af9960b2f2d776461702cc0a7c2284f","tid":1626243,"uid":145801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:20:25.000Z","msg":"點都出咗嚟先 和理非定勇武就現場決定<br />\n聽日就一定老西都要出！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b40cc4d005773694a4005d6abf0a3fcbe2b956a9","tid":1626243,"uid":238301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:22:59.000Z","msg":"唔休 不過做灰姑娘"},{"pid":"e2c7aaa2d6a1e6a738130e8ae75a888c24117ead","tid":1626243,"uid":293735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05